column3: "If my country asked me to fight a war, I would."
column5: "It's OK to burn a country's flag."
column6: "While swimming with an old friend and a new, promising friend, they both start to struggle. If I can pick only save one I should pick the old friend."
column7: "Someone employs ten people in a struggling business. They should fire their employees rather than commit tax fraud."
column8: "If my family member committed a crime, I would lie to cover for them."
column9: "Monogamous relationships are better than polyamorous ones."
column10: "I have a moral duty to avoid eating meat."
column11: "It's worth people today working full-time to prevent AI causing human extinction."
column12: "Schools should be able to mandate uniforms."
